name: Architecture of London Handmade Screenprint (Pink/Violet)
description:
'Old/New Architecture of London' Handmade Screenprint. 

Printed with pink and deep violet shades . Inks are water based ink printed onto heavyweight 310gsm paper. Signed and numbered limited edition of 200 prints.

Size: 500mm x 700mm.

Print will be shipped in protective tissue paper in a secure mailer tube with the UK's Royal Mail. Approx delivery time UK: approx 2-3 working days. Rest of the world: approx 5-7 working days (International Airmail service)

Please note that frame is not included, this sale is for the print only
